,"type":"paragraph"}],"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"OUDS iOS provides also a wiki attached to its GitHub repository. The wiki is a public base of knowledge with plenty of things: available API, technicala architecture, tips about processes, tests, conventions and toolings.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"code":null,"runtimePreview":null,"media":"tutorial-discovery-6-4.png","type":"step","caption":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"To get the source code of this showcase app, go to its dedicated GitHub repository at ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"https:\/\/github.com\/Orange-OpenSource\/ouds-ios-design-system-toolbox","type":"reference"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"For technical reasons the ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"https:\/\/github.com\/Orange-OpenSource\/ouds-ios","type":"reference"},{"text":" GitHub repository does not embed the source code of the ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"design system toolbox"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":" app. In fact this app and all its snapshots for tests increases a lot the size of the repository.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"code":null,"runtimePreview":null,"media":"tutorial-discovery-6-5.png","type":"step","caption":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Do not hesitate to ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"https:\/\/github.com\/Orange-OpenSource\/ouds-ios\/issues","type":"reference"},{"text":" or ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"https:\/\/github.com\/Orange-OpenSource\/ouds-ios\/discussions","type":"reference"},{"text":"!","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"OUDS is open source, public and uses GitHub as forge. Thus, you will find common things inside the ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"https:\/\/github.com\/Orange-OpenSource\/ouds-ios","type":"reference"},{"text":" GitHub repository.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"anchor":"More-reso